-912907647.text: "These results indicate that ALS significantly downregulates the expression of CDC2, cyclin B1, and CDK2 but upregulates p21 Waf1 and Cip1, p27 Kip1, and p53 in both PANC-1 and BxPC-3 cells, which contributes, at least in part, to the observed cell cycle arrest phenomenon in both cell lines."
